<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div>
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Price List &middot; Los Angeles &middot; 2026</p>
      <h1>Fireplace Repair Cost in Los Angeles</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Labor rates for gas, electric, and direct-vent fireplaces &mdash; indoor and outdoor. Thermopile, igniter, valve, burner issues. Gas safety check included on every call. Parts quoted separately.</p>
