            <td><div class="price-labor">$150&ndash;$280</div><div class="price-parts-note">+ igniter module or electrode</div></td>
            <td>Electronic igniter module, spark electrode, igniter wire. Moisture from coastal fog or infrequent use is a common cause in LA.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><div class="repair-type">Gas valve failure <span class="gas-badge">GAS</span></div><div class="repair-desc">Gas not flowing, or flowing uncontrolled</div></td>
            <td><div class="price-labor">$250&ndash;$420</div><div class="price-parts-note">+ gas valve assembly</div></td>
            <td>Gas valve replacement. We confirm thermopile output and supply pressure are adequate before diagnosing the valve &mdash; a good valve can appear failed if the thermopile output is low. Post-replacement leak test required.</td>
